			<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=100790&amp;sid=470b914aba49a934753461ce7dc19d56#100790"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Dec 06, 2004 7:29 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Author wins lawsuit for stolen Matrix script</span></td>
				<td width="30%" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap" align="right"> <a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=100790&amp;sid=470b914aba49a934753461ce7dc19d56"><img src="templates/eqluclin/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td></tr></table></td>
